<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-07-0818 </DOCNO><TEXT>Neutron-radiation analysis (NRA) facility with californium source of neutronsis described. Selection of the optimal geometric parameters and protectionelements is substantiated experimentally. The possibility to use NRAfor element analysis of iron-manganese nodules of the most importan elements- Mn, Fe, Co - is shown.</TEXT></DOC>